channel.title: Thread hasn't appeared yet?
channel.description:
So, I made a thread in the server dev. section yesterday, and yet it hasn't appeared yet.. Should I assume that it's supposed to be approved first due to my >2000 post count, or what?
I also tried to message the mods in control of the section, but it just said that I didn't have permission for it.
edit: interestingly enough this thread posts and yet my other one doesn't.. not sure if should re-post..
